Full Termux instalation process, just copy these commands and paste in Termux terminal and if it ask for "Y or N", "Y, N, O, D" or whatever, choose only "Y".
1. termux-setup-storage
2. pkg update
3. (if after "pkg update" it says "12 packages can be upgraded. Run 'apt list --upgradable' to see them.", ignore it)
4. pkg install apt
5. pkg install ca-certificates
6. pkg install command-not-found
7. pkg install debianutils
8. pkg install less
9. pkg install libandroid-support
10. pkg install libgcrypt
11. pkg install liblz4
12. pkg install libnghttp3
13. pkg install libunbound
14. pkg install patch
15. pkg install termux-keyring
16. apt update
17. apt upgrade
18. pkg up -y
19. apt install git
20. pkg install wget
21. pkg install python
22. pkg install python2
23. pkg install python3
